{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Sever diplomatic, trade, and other relations with Israel and impose sanctions",
        "additional_details": "We think this is needed because of many concerns about Israel's actions. A UN Independent International Commission of Inquiry found that Israel has committed genocide.",
        "background": "Government should sever diplomatic relations with Israel, suspend all imports from and exports to Israel (including of military equipment & components), impose tight economic sanctions, cancel any contracts with Israeli firms (including UK subsidiaries) & cease any intelligence sharing with Israel.",
